HEADWORD: inhibiting
<hw>inhibiting</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>discouraging (a person) from
action by threat of punishment; <as>as, an overly strict or
<ex>inhibiting</ex> discipline</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> inhibitory, repressive, repressing.</syn>⟦br⟧
